# Homepage Preservation Rule

- Keep the unauthenticated landing homepage in `app/page.tsx` pixel-identical to the original baseline design.
- Do not change hero image, title image, text spacing, mask/overlay, card copy, or contact-info layout unless the user explicitly requests homepage redesign.
- For other feature updates, avoid modifying homepage sections; scope edits to auth flow, form tabs, APIs, and components outside the landing block.
- If a requested change risks touching homepage layout, confirm first and apply minimal diff.
